{
  "stem": "26609.13",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Even to the Ukrainians, they didn't give to the hospital anything, no food delivered.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I don't know what they had said, how they lived there, and many children died at the hospital.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And as I looked further-- I didn't want to go away-- I felt I must see my child.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And then I had another look and she smiled.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "She-- I didn't recognize her, but she smiled.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "It wasn't a smile.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "It was just thin white line here, but I noticed that she smiled to me.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "She recognized me, because I was the same, but she was not the same.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I do anything you want, please.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Do it for me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I promised her that I will be her sister after the war.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Maybe it will be different.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I will help her if I-- if it will be possible.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And somehow, I convinced her and she went.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And a few hours later, she brought her home, brought her to me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I didn't have anything.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I couldn't give her-- she was still not well.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "She hardly could speak.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "She needed different care as a sick child.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But in those circumstances, I couldn't do anything.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I hugged her.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And as I stood there and thought what to do, although I couldn't do anything.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "She said to me, I can't keep you both here, or-- you or you're child.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And as you have been-- because before, I've been in prison, [NON-ENGLISH], as you have been in prison, those-- the police who went after you, they will recognize you, and they will-- if they see you, you'll lead them to my place.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They will go after you and come in here, and see your child here, and start questioning, whose child is it?",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
